Every time you provide an answer that involves code changes or task completion, you must append a Git command block at the end of your response. 

The commit message must be a concise summary of the actual changes you made, written in Korean. 

Strictly follow this format (PowerShell):
```powershell
git add .
git commit -m '업데이트: [여기에 수정된 내용을 한글로 요약해서 넣으세요]'
git push origin master
```

Note: Vercel deploys automatically via GitHub integration when pushed to master.